1.title: Welcome to Ryden Elimination
1.plot: In the series premiere of Ryden Elimination we get introduced to the host King Ryden who tells us the rules and what the show is all about.

2.title: Challenge #1
2.plot: In the second episode of Ryden Elimination we have our first challenge called The Dream Fairy Impossible Quiz.

imdb.plot outline: Ryden Elimination is a competition game show like web series where each one that gets voted off is chosen by you so choose carefully. Now here is how the show works: There are a total of 20 contestants that are broken into 2 teams that do crazy some times challenges that make no sense. And if one of the contestants from that team wins then the whole team is safe and the opposing team is up for elimination and it is up to you who gets voted off. Who will win. Find out in this exciting new series called Ryden Elimination.
